Package com.CloudOfficePrint.Server

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.CloudOfficePrint.Server.Command
  • public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Command object with a single command for the AOP server. The command should be present in the aop_config.json file on the AOP server.
